OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Lauren
OL,7,FOstridge went behind the scenes at the
OL,8,Fprogramme aimed at those who carry out
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse, whose supporters say
OL,10,Fhas had remarkable results.
OL,12,FA man who attacked his wife pushing
OL,13,Fher to the ground and strangling her
OL,14,Fsays he has been able to change his
OL,15,Fways thanks to a scheme which
OL,16,Fconfronts abusers with the reality of
OL,17,Ftheir behaviour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
