OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,FMichael - who has chosen a different
OL,7,Fname to protect his and his family's
OL,8,Fidentities - says he became violent
OL,9,Fafter an argument erupted over money.
OL,11,FThe dad referred himself to a
OL,12,Fperpetrator intervention scheme in
OL,13,FManchester called Bridging to Change,
OL,14,Frun by the charity Talk, Listen,
OL,15,FChange.
OL,17,FIts aim is to help people who have
OL,18,Fbeen abusive in the past to reform by
OL,19,Funderstanding why they use violence or
OL,20,Faggression in relationships, and build
OL,21,Fthe emotional skills to change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
