OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,F"You look at your life and you realise
OL,7,Fsomething needs to change," he said.
OL,9,F"Social services took me away from my
OL,10,Fkids so I did some research and found
OL,11,Fthe programme.
OL,13,F"I'm now aware of when I'm getting
OL,14,Fstressed and I know that I can't take
OL,15,Fthat out on other people - especially
OL,16,Fmy wife.
OL,18,F"I'm mindful about my presence around
OL,19,Fwomen and my kids - which I never was
OL,20,Fbefore."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
