OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,FMartin, who has also changed his name,
OL,7,Fwas arrested after he was violent
OL,8,Ftowards his partner. He says his home
OL,9,Fused to be a toxic environment.
OL,11,F"It was my way or nothing," he said.
OL,12,F"You don't realise how much your anger
OL,13,Faffects your children.
OL,15,F"Everyone would walk on eggshells
OL,16,Faround me - not knowing how I'd react.
OL,18,F"Thinking about it now it's
OL,19,Fheartbreaking. To think that I put my
OL,20,Ffamily through that.
