OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,FThe charity says it has seen huge
OL,7,Fresults, with research commissioned by
OL,8,Fthe Home Office shows when Bridging to
OL,9,FChange referrals were matched to
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police data,
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse incidents reduced by
OL,12,F80% for those that complete the
OL,13,Fprogramme.
OL,15,F"The victim is always very much in our
OL,16,Fminds, it's always about the victim,
OL,17,Fand about the children and about
OL,18,Fsafety, that's the basic thing," Tony
OL,19,FSheppard, a domestic abuse prevention
OL,20,Fworker, said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
