OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,F"We know if we can intervene with the
OL,7,Fmen when there's been domestic abuse
OL,8,Fthen the victim is going to be safe."
OL,10,FSarah Townsend, another domestic abuse
OL,11,Fprevention worker, added: "So many
OL,12,Ftimes I thought men who were
OL,13,Fperpetrators could not change because
OL,14,Fof the background they came from.
OL,16,F"When I see it I'm always overjoyed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
