OL,6,FSince 2017, 3,092 men have been
OL,7,Freferred to the sessions, but, despite
OL,8,Fits success it is one of a dwindling
OL,9,Fnumber of perpetrator intervention
OL,10,Fschemes.
OL,12,F"The government are really putting
OL,13,Fthings in place to make working with
OL,14,Fperpetrators at the top of the
OL,15,Fagenda," Lisa Wilkie, head of domestic
OL,16,Fabuse at Talk, Listen, Change said.
OL,18,F"But we've got a long way to go and
OL,19,Fwhile we're got a long way to go
OL,20,Ffunding is like a postcode lottery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
