OL,3,CDad who strangled wife says charity
OL,4,Chelped him confront his domestic abuse
OL,6,F"Each local authority should have
OL,7,Ftheir own funding and that's just not
OL,8,Fthe case."
OL,10,FWhen questioned whether "someone like
OL,11,Fhim" deserves a second chance, Michael
OL,12,Fsaid he believes everyone does.
OL,14,F"This course is intensive. It makes
OL,15,Fyou look at every aspect of your life
OL,16,Fand how your actions can impact
OL,17,Fothers," Michael said.
OL,19,F"I think you can learn to change."
